name: Route 66
overview: A freeware puzzle game created in 1993 and updated in 1994 by Ekke Verheul of ASWare. It was included in the Assassins 219 game pack along with Chopper Attack and Gimme 5. Travel through a world of roads. Use the arrow keys to walk around and try to get filthy rich fast. In most cases there is one UNDO possible and I know you're gonna use it!
